Original Author: chuonthis &lt;a href="http://outgoing.mozilla.org/v1/3e7cc272a31ec888f4a340fc1b92f65281bcb7a1/http%3A//www.chuonthis.com/extensions/"&gt;http://www.chuonthis.com/extensions/&lt;/a&gt;
