New feature: version 2.8.0.1 or higher can export messages in HTML/plain text format with attachments.

Moreover it has an option to have a scheduled backup of all profile's files or just of mail files.
For more details visit &lt;a href="http://outgoing.mozilla.org/v1/de932d5086b7c9b7bb399c4a4f09181a3d2ba3c2407a062088df6aec4de8a827/https%3A//nic-nac-project.org/%7Ekaosmos/mboximport-en.html" rel="nofollow"&gt;https://nic-nac-project.org/~kaosmos/mboximport-en.html&lt;/a&gt;

In my website you can find lots of extensions and maybe some of them could interest you, so have a peek.

